::Striker/Prowl::

Striker nods, raising an eyebrow.

"Are you going to give him the comp?" he asks, watching Iron Raptor carefully 
for the answer. He had his own way of dealing with things, but was curious 
what hers was.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl walks up to Beachbomber, looking at the unconscious Smokescreen.

"Here, get his other side," he says, lifting Smokescreen's left hand to his 
shoulder.
